                <p class="flex justify-between"><span>Saturday:</span> <span class="font-medium text-gray-800">9:00 AM - 12:00 PM</span></p>
                <p class="flex justify-between"><span>Sunday:</span> <span class="text-gray-400">Closed</span></p>
